text: Évry-Courcouronnes is a new commune in the Essonne department in France. The commune was founded on 1 January 2019. Évry and Courcouronnes joined to make this new commune. The Genopole is in the city. == Education == * Institut Mines-Télécom Business School == References == ==Other websites== Category:2019 establishments in France
